```python
def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('F', 'Fm')

print(insert_after_character('Hello F World'))
print(insert_after_character('Fruit flies'))
print(insert_after_character('F'))
print(insert_after_character('No F in this string'))
print(insert_after_character('FFFFF'))
```
